title: Week 16 preview & Giants vs Eagles recap
itunes:title: Week 16 preview & Giants vs Eagles recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game previewing each week 16 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night NFC East matchup between the Giants and the Eagles.
